{"tid":1652291,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"為確保明年美國總統大選順利，微軟將持續免費更新 Windows 7，確保投票系統能順利運作，防止駭客攻擊。","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T19:32:38.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9568bdf101ed7df088dc943ecc23432c7147a72f","tid":1652291,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"早前微軟 Microsoft 已確定 Windows 7 於 2020 年 1 月 14 日停止更新，讓這個在 2009 年推出，被不少電腦用家視為近年最實用的作業系統，劃上完美句號。然而，Windows 7 任務還未完的，只因 Microsoft 決定網開一面延長 Windows 7 免費安全更新，確保 2020 年美國總統大選時，聯邦認證投票系統能運作順利，選民能安心投選心儀總統候選人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2455000/2457663/win7_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2455000%2F2457663%2Fwin7_1024.jpg&h=af3b3001&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">Microsoft 將延長 Windows 7 免費安全更新\n確保 2020 年美國總統大選聯邦認證投票系統運作順利\n品牌理解在 2020 年美國總統大選前，未必有足夠時間更新投票系統為最新版本</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n對於 Microsoft 延長 Windows 7 免費安全更新的舉動，全國州務卿協會 NASS 發言人表示，品牌此舉確讓不少人受惠，例如選民可以順利投選心儀總統候選人，不過數碼保安顧問 Kevin Skoglund 則認為此舉各有優缺。他認為能提供延長 Windows 7 免費安全更新，固然是好事，可是當中卻沒法解決投票系統認證程序緩慢的問題。縱然 Windows 10 的更新作業系統經已遞交予美國聯邦政府審批，但當中能否趕及明年美國總統大選，仍是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2457663/Microsoft%20%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%20Windows%207%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%20%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2457663%2FMicrosoft%2520%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%2520Windows%25207%2520%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%2520%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%25A0%2586%25E5%2588%25A9&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=9016907a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2457663/Microsoft%20%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%20Windows%207%20%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%20%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9</a>"},{"pid":"9337b72e6ee81a3c63110e09115280353da5ee19","tid":1652291,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2591239227e57ef1ec26b7a66f1aea9eadaa5cdc","tid":1652291,"uid":226562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"改用 android/linux 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmsft收咗幾多錢"},{"pid":"7da058c0aac0326611caa3620d7462885bf68863","tid":1652291,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2591239227e57ef1ec26b7a66f1aea9eadaa5cdc","tid":1652291,"uid":226562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"改用 android/linux 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmsft收咗幾多錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:34:13.000Z","msg":"時間同金錢成本比起沿用現有系統更大"},{"pid":"16329d195403734009f334997119a283cd68ae45","tid":1652291,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2591239227e57ef1ec26b7a66f1aea9eadaa5cdc","tid":1652291,"uid":226562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"改用 android/linux 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmsft收咗幾多錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201